* The Grill Room: On the latest edition of the podcast, my friend and Puck =
partner John Ourand stopped by to preview Super Bowl weekend in New Orleans=
, and to assess the verisimilitude of Chiefs fatigue. We also dove into the=
 latest live-sports-rights developments, and explored how streaming giants =
like Amazon and Netflix are reshaping the future of sports broadcasting. Pl=
us, we offered our thoughts on Tom Brady=E2=80=99s progress in the broadcas=
